locations.description: TunnelEstablishmentProtocol implements IKEv2 with DH key exchange
locations.evidence: Internet Key Exchange, Diffie-Hellman groups, IPSec SA negotiation

locations.description: TunnelEncryption implements AES-256-GCM for VPN traffic
locations.evidence: Galois Counter Mode, 256-bit key, authenticated encryption

locations.description: CertificateAuthentication implements RSA for VPN certificates
locations.evidence: RSA certificate verification, PKI authentication, X.509 certificates

locations.description: EllipticKeyAgreement implements ECDH for ephemeral keys
locations.evidence: P-384 curve, ephemeral key generation, perfect forward secrecy

locations.description: TunnelIntegrityProtection implements HMAC for packet authentication
locations.evidence: keyed hash function, packet integrity, IPSec ESP authentication

risk_assessment.recommendation: Replace IKEv2, RSA, and ECDH with post-quantum alternatives for VPN security
